

# <type>(<scope>): <short summary>
# <description>
# 
# <short summary> is in present tense, not capitalized and has no period at the end.
# <description> is optional.
# <scope> is optional.
# <type> is
#     build:    changes that affect the build system
#     chore:    routine maintenance, tooling, dependency updates, or other non-production changes
#     ci:       changes to CI configuration files and scripts
#     docs:     documentation only changes
#     feat:     a new feature
#     fix:      a bug fix
#     perf:     a code change that improves performance
#     refactor: a code change that neither fixes a bug nor adds a feature
#     style:    changes that do not affect the meaning of the code (e.g. formatting, whitespace)
#     test:     adding missing tests or correcting existing tests
#